      <pre style="font: 9pt Courier New, Tahoma, MS Sans Serif, Microsoft Sans Serif, Verdana, AngsanaUPC, CordiaUPC; padding: 10px;">
        SET adds new listed securities : TSC

The Stock Exchange of Thailand (SET) reported that the SET's 
board has granted a listing of common shares of  THAI STEEL
CABLE  Public Company Limited  from June 23, 2005 onwards.

The SET has set common shares of  THAI STEEL CABLE
 Public Company Limited, amounting to 259,800,000 shares with  
a par value of  Baht 1 per share, to be traded on the SET under the
group of Industrials, Automotive sector and using the trading name 
of  "TSC"  commencing from June 23, 2005.

Note: Please see the Information Memorandum of  TSC
disseminated on the SET Market Analysis and Reporting Tool
(SETSMART) and website: http://www.thaisteelcable.com

                                                          Information Memorandum
                           THAI STEEL CABLE PUBLIC COMPANY LIMITED (TSC)

Head Office:    
         57 Moo 6, Kingkaew Road, Rachataewa, Bangplee, Samutprakarn 10540 Thailand Tel. 0-2738-9460-76 
Fax 0-2326-6237, 0-2738-9482 Website: http://www.thaisteelcable.com

Factory Location:       
         57 Moo 6, Kingkaew Road, Rachataewa, Bangplee, Samutprakarn 10540 Thailand  Tel. 0-2738-9460-76 
Fax 0-2326-6237, 0-2738-9482 Website: http://www.thaisteelcable.com

Listing Date                   As at June 23, 2005 (Trading commencement on June 23, 2005) 

Listing Securities            No. of common shares    259,800,000 shares
                                        Par value per share     1 Baht
                                       Total value     THB 259.80 Million

Secondary Market          SET

Offering Price                 THB 9.20 per share

Offering Period              June 15 - 16, 2005

Type of Business and Nature of Operation
         Thai Steel Cable Public Company Limited ("the Company") is an auto parts manufacturer (both OEM and REM) 
whose main customers  are automobile &  motorcycle manufacturers their respective service centers, and auto parts 
manufacturers located in both Thailand and abroad. The Company's customers also include companies in the Nippon
Cable System Inc Group., which is TSC's Japanese partner and major shareholder.  The Company has 2 main product
categories as per the followings.
         1.  Control Cable
             -  Automobile Control Cable i.e. Hood Release Cable, Trunk Opener Cable, Accelerator Cable, Transmission 
Cable
             -  Motorcycle Control Cable i.e. Brake Cable, Clutch Cable, Tachometer Cable, Throttle Cable

         2.  Window Regulator i.e. Cable-type window regulator and x-arm type window regulator for all kinds of 
automobiles 
             The Company produces the above listed control cables and cable-type window regulators under the License
and Technical Assistance Agreement entered into between the Company and Nippon Cable System Inc., a leading 
manufacturer of control cables for motor vehicle in Japan and the Company's major shareholder.  In addition, the 
Company also entered into the Technical License  Agreement to produce x-arm type window regulator with a 
Japanese firm called Fuji Kiko Company Limited.

             The Company has a maximum production capacity of approximately 6 million automobile control cables, 15 
million motorcycle  control cables and 1.5 million window regulators (in aggregate of both cable-type and x-arm type
window regulator).

